@bijart\_dauth  
The Urzatron are not eclipsed by [cloudpost](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=cloudpost). Cloudpost is only a single card and thus you can have only 1 playset in the deck. Furthermore, coming into play tapped is a huge disadvantage.   
These can be played in any artifact deck as though they were basic lands.

